results.name: Decimal expansion of a constant related to A000294.
comment: The unknown constant C from articles by Finch (p.2), resp. c3(m) by Mustonen and Rajesh (p.2).
link: Steven Finch, Integer Partitions, September 22, 2004, page 2. [Cached copy, with permission of the author].
Ville Mustonen and R. Rajesh, Numerical Estimation of the Asymptotic Behaviour of Solid Partitions of an Integer, J. Phys. A 36 (2003), no. 24, 6651-6659.
formula: Equals Pi^(1/24) * exp(1/24 - Zeta(3) / (8*Pi^2) + 75*Zeta(3)^3 / (2*Pi^8)) / (A^(1/2) * 2^(157/96) * 15^(13/96)), where A = A074962 is the Glaisher-Kinkelin constant and Zeta(3) = A002117.
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Mar 11 2015
